data.description: Right in front of the Grove Park sits this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom, 3 story condo in the planned neighborhood of Tosara in Chula Vista's Montecito Community! Within walking distance to the Muraoka (saburo) Elementary and Otay Ranch Senior High School. Enjoy a gated front courtyard entry to wood flooring, ceiling fans, and a gourmet kitchen. The kitchen offers granite countertops, a breakfast bar, and stainless steel appliances. The primary bedroom features a walk-in closet, dual vanities in the primary bathroom, a soaking tub, and a separate walk-in shower. Additional property highlights include a full-size laundry room, tankless water heater and a 2 car garage. Community amenities include a swimming pool, spa, basketball courts and recreation room. Nearby top rated schools, parks, shopping plazas, and easy access to freeways and shops.
